{
  "id": "adv_event_2209_01_02",
  "title": "ミクの記念日",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku001.m4a",
      "text": "初めまして、初音ミクです\nTRINITYAiLEのみんな、よろしくね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hi‚ I'm Hatsune Miku.\nNice to meet you all‚ TRINITYAiLE!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.1380272865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "凄い……これ、ホログラムって技術ですか？\n確かに、顔合わせが出来てる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amazing… Is this hologram technology?\nWe can meet like this..wow….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.3333333333,
      "endTime": 14.777641900299999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku002.m4a",
      "text": "私からも、みんなのこと、ちゃんと見えてるよ\n天動瑠依ちゃん、鈴村優ちゃん、奥山すみれちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can see everyone properly from my side too.\nRui Tendo-chan‚ Yu Suzumura-chan‚ Sumire Okuyama-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.9666666667,
      "endTime": 24.972607867,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "うっ！　本物のミクちゃんから名前呼ばれた……\nうち、幸せ者過ぎるやろ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh! Being called by the real Miku-chan…\nI'm so lucky…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.1666666667,
      "endTime": 33.204807249699996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "こちらこそ初めまして、ミクちゃん！\nそれにしても、凄い機械だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you too‚ Miku-chan!\nThis is an amazing machine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.4,
      "endTime": 39.6385943413,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "普段、初音さんがライブステージに立つ時も\n同じような原理の機械を使ってるそうだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Normally‚ when Hatsune-san performs on the live stage…\nThey use a similar principle with the machine‚ I heard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8333333333,
      "endTime": 45.3576418241,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n呼ぶ時はミクでいいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san.\nYou can call me Miku.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.5666666667,
      "endTime": 49.860498778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか。分かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "O-Okay‚ got it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0666666667,
      "endTime": 52.765283457500004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku004.m4a",
      "text": "私はネットワークの世界に生きてるからね\nいろんなデバイスを、自由に行き来出来るんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I live in the network world‚ you see.\nI can freely move between various devices.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.9666666667,
      "endTime": 60.9292519252,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "だから、バーチャル・シンガーっていうんだ\nでも……やっぱり触れられないのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's why they call youo a virtual singer.\nBut… still can't be physically touched.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.1333333333,
      "endTime": 67.1569613774,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "あくまでも投影されてる状態やからなぁ\nただ、こうしてお話し出来るだけでも十分やんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ she is just being projected.\nBut being able to have this conversation is already enough‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.3666666667,
      "endTime": 75.17975060149999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku005.m4a",
      "text": "歌を届けるのに、必ずしも体は必要じゃないからね\n今のままでも、出来ることは沢山あるんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't necessarily need a physical body to deliver my songs.\nEven in this form‚ there are plenty of things I can do.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3666666667,
      "endTime": 85.011337916,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、そうかもしれないわね\n……改めてよろしくね、ミク",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might be true.\n…Nice to meet you again‚ Miku!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.2,
      "endTime": 91.0493879318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "さて。この前も伝えたけど、トリエルの三人には\nマジカルミライに出演してもらう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then. As I mentioned before‚\nTRINITYAiLE is going to perform at Magical Mirai.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2333333333,
      "endTime": 96.8663716633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "ミクちゃんのライブに出演かぁ\nずっと観る側やったから、嬉しいし感慨深いわぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To perform at Miku-chan's live. It's both exciting\nand emotional for me‚ since I've always been on the watching side.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.0666666667,
      "endTime": 105.304013602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mku",
      "speakerName": "初音ミク",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hatsune",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-mku006.m4a",
      "text": "改めて、出演を決めてくれてありがとう！\nみんなが出演してくれたら、絶対素敵なライブになるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you once again for deciding to perform!\nIt will be a fantastic concert with everyone's participation.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.5,
      "endTime": 114.3217237473,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "ミクちゃんからのオファーだもん、断れないよ！\nお祝いの気持ち、いーっぱい届けるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We can't refuse an offer from Miku-chan!\nWe'll express lots of celebration and support.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.5333333333,
      "endTime": 121.3386848767,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "曲構成はどうするん？　うちらの既存曲を\nただ歌うだけなんは、なんや申し訳ないなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about the song arrangement?\nIt feels a bit inadequate if we just sing our existing songs…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.5333333333,
      "endTime": 129.632788976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "ミクの曲をカバーしたり、でしょうか？\nもちろん、対応は可能ですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are we going to cover Miku's songs‚ perhaps?\nOf course‚ we can do that…But..",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.8333333333,
      "endTime": 135.89684785210002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "いや、今回は新曲をつくろうと思ってるんだ\nミクの記念日をお祝いする楽曲の予定だ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ this time I'm thinking of creating a new song.\nIt will be a commemorative song for Miku's anniversary.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.1,
      "endTime": 142.18743743890002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "ほんまに！？　めっちゃ嬉しいわぁ\n8月31日といえばミクちゃんの記念日やもんなぁ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really!? I'm so excited!\nAugust 31‚ that's Miku-chan's anniversary!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4,
      "endTime": 150.6033107758,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "確かに私達、お祝いの曲ってやったことなかったね\nイベントにもピッタリだし、楽しみ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's true‚ we've never done a celebratory song before.\nIt's perfect for that event‚ and I'm looking forward to it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.8,
      "endTime": 159.07269821170001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "そして、もう一つ……\n新曲の作詞は、三人に任せたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And one more thing…\nI want the three of you to write the lyrics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.2666666667,
      "endTime": 164.3705216091,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "私達が作詞を……ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Are you asking us to write the lyrics…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 164.5666666667,
      "endTime": 168.1434012572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。想いを込めて、自分達で書いてもらいたい\nせっかくの機会だ。挑戦してみてもいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I want you to write them with your own feelings.\nIt's a great opportunity. Why not give it a try?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 168.3333333333,
      "endTime": 176.9158278783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "一理あるなぁ\nうちらの純粋な気持ちを込められるし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That makes sense.\nWe can pour our pure feelings into it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.1,
      "endTime": 182.0887526512,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "作詞ってしたことないし、いい経験になりそう！\nやってみようよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've never written lyrics before‚ so it will be a good experience!\nLet's give it a try.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 182.3,
      "endTime": 187.7709299087,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui006.m4a",
      "text": "……そうね\n自分達の想いを自分達で形にする、いい機会よね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Yes.\nIt's a good opportunity for us to express our own feelings.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 187.9666666667,
      "endTime": 195.74986387890002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui007.m4a",
      "text": "分かりました\n作詞、私達にやらせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood.\nPlease let us handle the lyrics.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 195.9333333333,
      "endTime": 200.51757357920002,
      "sfxList": []
