      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "決まりだな\nミクも、それでいいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's settled then.\nIs that okay with you‚ Miku?",
