      "text": "ふふっ……ミクちゃんの記念日をお祝いする曲の詞……\nうちに書かせてもらえるなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe… Writing lyrics for a song to celebrate Miku-chan's anniversary…\nI can't believe I will be the one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.8,
      "endTime": 217.6539684295,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
