      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2209_01_02-rui008.m4a",
      "text": "私達、ね\nほんと、優はミクのことになるとポンコツね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Not just you‚ us too.\nYou're such a klutz when it comes to Miku‚ Yu…",
